==Hindi==
===Etymology===
McGregor inferred it to be from Old Indo-Aryan ''dādda-''. Platts gives it as from the Sanskrit तात+कः

===Noun===
'''दादा''' ''dādā'' {{m}}
# paternal [[grandfather]]
# respectful address for an older man

===Reference===
*McGregor, R.S, ed. ''The Oxford Hindi-English Dictionary'', Oxford university press. 1993

